%% Diagram: Facebook lease pattern for stampede prevention
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client 1
    participant C2 as Client 2
    participant Cache
    participant DB

    C1->>Cache: GET key
    Cache-->>C1: miss + lease token L1
    Note right of Cache: Lease throttles fetches per key
    C2->>Cache: GET key
    Cache-->>C2: hot-miss, wait or retry

    C1->>DB: SELECT key
    DB-->>C1: value
    C1->>Cache: SET key value with lease L1
    Cache-->>C1: stored

    C2->>Cache: GET key (retry)
    Cache-->>C2: value (populated)

    Note over Cache,DB: A DELETE between fetch and SET invalidates the lease and rejects the stale write
